<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>A Na Ta Luoi</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka Lal thawkna ka ngaihtuoh in,
 Kah lohna guol ei puoi;
 A mai a betnau leh, liemna A thawkna chu,
 Ka ngaihtuoh ni hin chu naubang ka kap

[V2]
 A na taluoi ! ei tatna,(2)
 Khawvel Hukdampa chu;
 A luong a chieh pih tau,
 I Lal lungnem a hi gimthei mahleh.

[V3]
 2. Juda mipiten mawhchang in,
 Hun na guot mahleule;
 Ken vang ka hun ngai ie, ka Lal lungnem Na hi,
 Keihaw gitloh ziekin tha Na kie tai,

[V4]
 3. Nei zo thakie mi'n a gal un,
 Van Lal thi a gal puou;
 Thihna'n nau bang a awi, I Lal lungsiet um pau,
 Than sungah a siel ui mi et nuom loh

[V5]
 4. A thokit tai, I Lalpau chu,
 Chawlhna gam zuon dingin;
 Olive tang chunga meipi'n a puito in.
 Chawlhna gam A zuon tai, I Lalpau chun.

[V6]
 5. Chawlhna gam na zawt tak ziekin,
 Khawvel a ngui zo tai;
 Hung kitin aw Lalpa khawvel dahum ahin,
 Nei tatna thugen in, nunnuom ungkau.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>78</hymn_number>
<author>V.T. Kappu</author>
</song>